will show all the groups and user connected to the groups
------------------------------

cat /etc/group   :will show all groups and user connected
groups  :this command lis the groiups u are connected
usdo groupadd java  :will add java as group
sudo gpasswd -a username grpname    :will add user to the grp . -a is for add and -d for remove user from grp
